CANVAS & LAYOUT
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Canvas:
- Orientation: vertical
- Aspect ratio: 3:4
- Background: warm neutral, paper-like surface

Layout structure:
- TOP SECTION: lifestyle hero image
- BOTTOM SECTION: technical specification panel

The layout must feel:
- editorial
- architectural
- modular
- balanced
- breathable

